# Personal Blog - Product Requirements Document

## Overview
A minimalist personal blog focused on content and readability. The blog features a clean, typography-focused design that puts the content first.

## User Stories

### As a Reader
- I want to read blog posts in a clean, distraction-free environment so that I can focus on the content.
- I want to easily navigate between posts so that I can discover more content.
- I want the blog to be responsive and readable on all devices so that I can read comfortably anywhere.

### As an Author (Admin)
- I want to write and publish blog posts easily so that I can focus on creating content.
- I want to edit and update existing posts so that I can maintain and improve my content.
- I want to manage my posts through a simple admin interface.

## Features

### Core Features
- **Homepage:**
  - Clean, minimalist design
  - List of recent blog posts
  - Clear navigation
  - Responsive layout

- **Blog Post Page:**
  - Typography-focused design
  - Clear hierarchy
  - Comfortable reading experience
  - Responsive images
  - Code block formatting

- **Admin Interface:**
  - Secure login
  - Post creation and editing
  - Markdown support
  - Preview functionality
  - Post management

### Technical Requirements
- Next.js App Router
- TypeScript
- Supabase for backend
- Responsive design
- SEO optimization
- Fast loading times
- Secure authentication
- Markdown support

## Design Philosophy
- Content-first approach
- Clean, minimalist aesthetic
- Typography-focused
- Responsive and accessible
- Fast and performant

## Success Metrics
- Page load times under 2 seconds
- Mobile-friendly score above 90
- Accessibility score above 90
- User engagement metrics
- Content readability scores 